      • BREAK_BLOCK

        public static final ParticleType BREAK_BLOCK
        This particle type will play the effect of a block that is being broken and it's break sound.

        This type has limited ParticleOptions, only ParticleOptions.BLOCK_STATE and ParticleOptions.ITEM_STACK_SNAPSHOT are supported.

      • FERTILIZER

        public static final ParticleType FERTILIZER
        This particle type will play the effect that will occur when a Player uses bone meal on a plant to boost the growth.

        This type has limited ParticleOptions, only ParticleOptions.QUANTITY is supported.

        This type can no longer be spawned on air blocks. It will only show up if spawned at the location of solid blocks.

      • FIREWORKS

        public static final ParticleType FIREWORKS
        This particle type will play a fireworks effect.

        This type has limited ParticleOptions, only ParticleOptions.FIREWORK_EFFECTS is supported.

      • FIRE_SMOKE

        public static final ParticleType FIRE_SMOKE
        This particle type will play the smoke particles of a fire.

        This type has limited ParticleOptions, only ParticleOptions.DIRECTION is supported.
